{"tid":1880242,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【義氣仔女古天樂】兩萬個口罩分發予長輩藝人","createTime":"2020-02-14T16:53:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T08:41:33.000Z","uid":175314,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a42df3abd0df42f4d4f70a3f154ca5bf8043605b","tid":1880242,"uid":175314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T16:53:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/209963/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%8F%A4%E5%A4%A9%E6%A8%82%E5%BF%83%E7%97%9B%E9%95%B7%E8%BC%A9%E8%97%9D%E4%BA%BA%E9%99%B7-%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E8%8D%92-%E5%9B%9B%E5%9C%8D%E6%80%A5%E6%92%B22%E8%90%AC%E5%80%8B%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E9%9B%AA%E4%B8%AD%E9%80%81%E7%82%AD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Ftopic%2Fdetail%2F209963%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%25A8%2582%25E5%25BF%2583%25E7%2597%259B%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%25BC%25A9%25E8%2597%259D%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2599%25B7-%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E8%258D%2592-%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%259C%258D%25E6%2580%25A5%25E6%2592%25B22%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E9%259B%25AA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%2580%2581%25E7%2582%25AD&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNgUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=686d3d1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/209963/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%8F%A4%E5%A4%A9%E6%A8%82%E5%BF%83%E7%97%9B%E9%95%B7%E8%BC%A9%E8%97%9D%E4%BA%BA%E9%99%B7-%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E8%8D%92-%E5%9B%9B%E5%9C%8D%E6%80%A5%E6%92%B22%E8%90%AC%E5%80%8B%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E9%9B%AA%E4%B8%AD%E9%80%81%E7%82%AD</a><br />\n<br />\n【義氣仔女古天樂】<br />\n兩萬個口罩分發予長輩藝人<br />\n<br />\n身為演藝人協會會長的古天樂，一直十分關心演藝界同業。眼見一眾年長藝人沒有口罩可用，於是他就想方設法四圍撲口罩，暫時找到2萬個口罩助他們解決困難。古天樂指這2萬個口罩已經分發到不同長輩藝人手上，同時亦會繼續撲口罩，如果能順利到貨會再派發。但他亦坦言，口罩能否送到來香港仍是未知之數，事關好多地方已經限制口罩出口。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">古仔真係好鳩過以前老強五台山美人嗰條肥撚多多聲，娛樂圈好跟紅頂白嘅，好多老前輩搵錢唔多餐搵餐食，短腳狗政協捐物資上大陸獻身，仲邊理香港呀，古仔自從做演藝人協會主席，自掏腰包幫香港藝人好多次，真 &middot; 義氣仔女。<br />\n</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f2b3bc6c65ec21860f1de3635bd706fb3b0a00d","tid":1880242,"uid":5737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T16:55:41.000Z","msg":"古仔 真係respect 既<br />\n作為前輩但香港都係走唔出<br />\n無casting 試鏡機會<br />\n永遠電影主角都係佢地幾位"},{"pid":"2bcc9ddb12545a0b91fda6eba457408bad577407","tid":1880242,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T17:09:38.000Z","msg":"咁就浪費左兩萬個口罩"},{"pid":"315e5a02cb907e30b9e0928e638b57aeff6d4cfb","tid":1880242,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T17:11:07.000Z","msg":"Yea, 又吹奏奶共藝人"},{"pid":"ee9366eac156b47db7bb815e832fdbd6c469bc1a","tid":1880242,"uid":175314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"315e5a02cb907e30b9e0928e638b57aeff6d4cfb","tid":1880242,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T17:11:07.000Z","msg":"Yea, 又吹奏奶共藝人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T17:19:33.000Z","msg":"佢又未算&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n點及王粗鹽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0902e32282e2f21c01c5ddbf4c8310811fff1e3f","tid":1880242,"uid":249263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T18:04:36.000Z","msg":"敬 古天樂為人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁的確佢真係見到有需要的人就去幫<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跪求大家唔好放棄國際線<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNgUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=ceb66029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><str